OL,6,FA homeowner who ignored planning
OL,7,Fpermission rules when building his
OL,8,Fhouse is appealing to planners to let
OL,9,Fhim keep some of its features.
OL,11,FThe man built his new five bedroom
OL,12,Fhome in Cockey Moor Road, in Bury,
OL,13,FGreater Manchester, too big and too
OL,14,Ftall, admitting that 'what is built is
OL,15,Fnot anywhere close to what was
OL,16,Fapproved.'
OL,18,FBury Council ordered Saeed Postchi to
OL,19,Fmake extensive alterations to the
OL,20,Fbuilding after it was 'not built in
OL,21,Faccordance with the plans'.
