OL,3,CHomeowner ignored planning laws and
OL,4,Cbuilt house 'too big and too tall'
OL,6,FBut after lowering the roof by 1.3
OL,7,Fmetres and removing a rear window to
OL,8,Fcomply with the original plans, Mr
OL,9,FPostchi has applied to the council to
OL,10,Flet him keep some of the other
OL,11,Fmodifications including an
OL,12,Foutbuilding, three patio style windows
OL,13,Fand first floor balconies.
OL,15,FAn enforcement notice issued by Bury
OL,16,FCouncil said: "It is materially
OL,17,Fdifferent in height, scale and massing.
